<title>Opera TV Emulator user guide</title>
<link>http://dev.opera.com/articles/view/opera-tv-emulator</link>
<author>Patrick H. Lauke</author>
<guid isPermaLink="true">http://dev.opera.com/articles/view/opera-tv-emulator</guid>
<pubDate>Wed, 23 Jan 2013 17:19:29 GMT</pubDate>
<description>The Opera TV Emulator allows web developer to test HTML5 and CE-HTML content for TVs and other appliances running the Opera Devices SDK, as well as HTML-based applications for the Opera TV Store. It comes packaged as an Oracle VirtualBox image and can be run on Windows, Mac and Linux.</description>
